<item>
            <title>[LU-15613] allow lfs_migrate to use &apos;cp&apos; instead of &apos;rsync&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15613</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs_migrate&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; is only copying a single file at a time, there is no real benefit from using &quot;&lt;tt&gt;rsync&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; as the only copytool.  Allow the copytool to be replaced by using the &lt;tt&gt;RSYNC&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;RSYNC_OPTS&lt;/tt&gt; environment variables to be specified, and add a short &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;cp&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; option to complement the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&amp;#45;&amp;#45;rsync&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; option with suitable options.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
